<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Yoru Cafe</title>
    <!-- link ke font awesome for inserting icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- link ke google fonts buat font -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair:ital,opsz,wght@0,5..1200,300..900;1,5..1200,300..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    

    <!-- link ke css -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- header -->
     <header>
        <div class="container header-container">    
            <a href="#" class="logo">
                <!-- Masukkin logo cafe disini -->
                 <i class="fa-solid fa-mug-hot logo-icon"></i>
                <div class="logo-text">Yoru <span>Cafe</span> </div>
            </a>

            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#Product">Product</li>
                    <li><a href="#">Location</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>

            <div class="nav-buttons">
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Sign In</a>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Order Online</a>
                </div>
            </div>
     </header>

     <!-- hero section -->
     <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <div class="hero-subtitle">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-seedling"></i>  
                    Ethically Sourced Beans
                </div>
                <h1 class="hero-title">Yoru Coffee<br><span>Dibuat Sepenuh Hati</span></h1>
                <p class="hero-text">Yoru Cafe adalah kafe bernuansa Jepang yang menghadirkan suasana hangat, tenang, dan nyaman untuk menemani setiap momenmu.</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="#products" class="btn btn-primary">Kunjungi Menu Kami</a>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Kunjungi Kafe Kami!</a>
                </div>
            </div>
             <img src="1.jpg" alt="" width="370px">
        </div>
        </section>
 
    <!-- Products Section -->
    <section class="products" id="products">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-subtitle">Menu Unggulan</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Kopi Khas Yoru Cafe</h2>
                <p class="section-desc">Temukan berbagai pilihan kopi khas Yoru Cafe yang dijamin memuaskan lidah Anda.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="product-grid">
            <div class="product-card">
                <div class="product-img">
                    <img src="2.jpg" alt="Moonveil">
                </div>
                <div class="product-info">
                    <div class="product-tag">Best Seller</div>
                    <h3 class="product-title">Moonveil</h3>
                    <p class="product-desc">Perpaduan espresso premium dengan susu creamy dan foam lembut, menciptakan rasa hangat yang halus di setiap tegukan.</p>
                    <div class="product-footer">
                        <div class="product-price">Rp 25.000</div>
                        <div class="Rating">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-star-half-stroke"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="product-card">
                    <div class="product-img">
                        <img src="3.jpg" alt="Night Whisper" width="736px" height="736px">
                    </div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-title">Night Whisper</h3>
                        <p class="product-desc">Sentuhan mocha dingin dengan rasa cokelat yang pekat dan creamy, dipadukan espresso lembut untuk menciptakan rasa manis yang hangat meski disajikan dingin.</p>
                        <div product-footer>
                            <div class="product-price">Rp 30.000</div>
                            <div class="Rating">
                             <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                             <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                             <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                             <i class="fa-solid fa-star-half-stroke"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="product-card">
                <div class="product-img">
                    <img src="4.jpg" alt="Shadow Roast" width="736px" height="736px">
                </div>
                <div class="product-info">
                    <div class="product-tag">New Arrival</div>
                    <h3 class="product-title">Shadow Roast</h3>
                    <p class="product-desc">Kopi hitam pekat dengan aroma yang kuat dan rasa yang kaya, memberikan pengalaman kopi yang intens dan memuaskan bagi para penikmat kopi sejati.</p>
                    <div class="product-footer">
                        <div class="product-price">Rp 20.000</div>
                        <div class="Rating">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section> 

        <!-- footer -->
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h3>Tentang Yoru Cafe</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--coffee-accent); margin-bottom: 20px;">Menyajikan rasa, suasana, dan kehangatan dalam setiap malam yang kamu habiskan di Yoru Cafe.</p>
                    <div class="social-links">
                        <a href="#"><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="fa-brands fa-tiktok"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h3>Quick Links</h3>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Menu</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Jl. Kenangan No. 123, Surabaya</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i> +62 812-3456-7890</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> YoruCafe@gmail.com</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i> Sen-Min: 08:00 - 23:00 WIB</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="copyright">
                &copy; 2025 Yoru Cafe. All rights reserved.
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- link ke javascript -->
    <script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
